---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Gamma PreQ - Acoustic Guitar Preamp, EQ & Boost"
  description="The Gamma PreQ is a DIY acoustic guitar preamp, EQ, and boost pedal designed by Ryan Schultz. Plenty of clean gain, flexible EQ, and a dedicated boost."
  ogImage="/images/pedals/gamma-preq2.jpeg"
  noindex={true}
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-brand-dark text-white py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-3">Gamma PreQ</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Acoustic Guitar Preamp, EQ &amp; Boost
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Image + description -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="md:flex gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="md:w-3/5 mb-8 md:mb-0">
          <img src="/images/pedals/gamma-preq2.jpeg" alt="Gamma PreQ acoustic guitar preamp pedal" class="rounded-xl shadow-lg w-full" />
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-2/5">
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4">Designed for Acoustic Guitar</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            The Gamma PreQ was designed specifically for acoustic guitar, although it will work for any acoustic instrument (but not bass). It has plenty of clean gain as a preamp, a plethora of EQ options, and a dedicated boost.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            It's quieter than most acoustic preamps and offers more EQ options. It's not as great as Grace Designs' ALiX (which is awesome), but it's close!
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            This is a <strong>DIY assembly</strong> you put together yourself. While this shouldn't be your first build, there's nothing particularly challenging about it other than its size (~150 total parts). Read the BOM and Build Notes carefully to comprehend the scope of this project.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-brand-warm">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl text-center mb-12">Features</h2>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-10">
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <li><strong>Gain, Volume, Boost:</strong> +25 dBu, +17 dBu, +6 dBu respectively
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1 text-gray-600">
              <li>-&infin; for Gain , Volume</li>
          </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>HPF / Notch:</strong> 68–440 Hz (Butterworth 2nd order)
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1 text-gray-600">
              <li>High Pass @ -12 dB/octave</li>
              <li>Notch: 5 &lt; Q &lt; 15</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li><strong>Low Control:</strong> @ 100 Hz +/- 12 dB</li>
          <li><strong>High Shelf:</strong> @ 4 kHz +/- 12 dB</li>
          <li>
            <strong>Parametric Mid:</strong> +/- 9 dB
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1 text-gray-600">
              <li>Low Range: 103 – 880 Hz, 0.5 &lt; Q &lt; 5</li>
              <li>High Range: 435 – 3700 Hz, 2 &lt; Q &lt; 20</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li><strong>Frequency Response:</strong> 68 Hz – 20 kHz</li>
          <li><strong>THD:</strong> &lt; 0.02 %</li>
          <li><strong>Input Power:</strong> &lt; 200 mA @ 9 VDC</li>
          <li><strong>Internal:</strong> +/-15 VDC — for plenty of headroom</li>
          <li><strong>Input Impedance:</strong> 1 MΩ</li>
          <li><strong>Bypass</strong>: True Bypass or Mute
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1 text-gray-600">
              <li>Internal switch</li>
          </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl mb-8">Pricing</h2>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-10 text-left">
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <li>
            <strong>PCB set only:</strong> $25 + $8 shipping
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Parts kit</strong> (no enclosure/knobs): $100 + $10 shipping
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1 text-gray-600">
              <li>+ $10 for 1 - LM4562</li>
              <li>+ $10 for 3 - OPA4134's</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>Payment via Venmo or PayPal</li>
        </ul>
          <img src="/images/pedals/gamma-pcb-set.jpeg" alt="Gamma PreQ acoustic guitar preamp pedal" class="rounded-xl shadow-lg w-full" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Documentation / Files -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-brand-warm">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl mb-4 text-center">Documentation</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg text-center mb-10">
        Reference documents for building and tuning the Gamma PreQ.
      </p>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-10">
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">

          <li>
            <a
              href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10XZUnoFiJfJFFmuHVIBVKQknY2kPwP4MDt2C2y5dbGs/edit?usp=drivesdk"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-brand-orange font-heading font-bold hover:underline"
            >
              BOM and Cost Estimate &rarr;
            </a>
          </li>

          <li>
            <a
              href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1bflPHyCgo-yc2phnAm6ZhRAkko28YN4nTb_pg0rxkQM/edit?usp=sharing"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-brand-orange font-heading font-bold hover:underline"
            >
              Build Notes & Schematics &rarr;
            </a>
          </li>

          <li>
            <a
              href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/120yCgvy48Y_ZRaOrTaf3OyHzmIOkdRPylhfyLCV6xtw/edit?tab=t.0"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-brand-orange font-heading font-bold hover:underline"
            >
              Circuit Notes &amp; Performance Plots &rarr;
            </a>
          </li>

          <li>
            <a
              href="https://drill.taydakits.com/box-designs/new?public_key=a2M0amFFNkFqWEhDTTY2elQ0RmE5UT09Cg=="
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-brand-orange font-heading font-bold hover:underline"
            >
              Tayda Drill Template &rarr;
            </a>
          </li>

          <li>
            <a
              href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/joulupukki/molinellomusic.com/main/src/pages/pedals/gamma-preq/GammaPreamp-v4.3-c.pdf"
              download="GammaPreamp-v4.3-c.pdf"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-brand-orange font-heading font-bold hover:underline"
            >
              Tayda UV Template &rarr;
            </a>
          </li>

        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact / Order -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl mb-4">Interested?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        If you have any questions about the build, get in touch.<br>
        To order PCB set or a parts kit:<br>
          <span class="text-sm leading-snug">
            - Specify what you want<br>
            - Paypal/Venmo address to invoice<br>
          </span>
      </p>

      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-block bg-brand-orange text-white font-heading font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-orange-600 transition-colors text-lg"
      >
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
